    "content": "I'm excited to share that I have accepted a position as General Contractor – Program Manager with Flock.\nOver the past several years, I've had the opportunity to build experience across construction operations, contractor licensing, regulatory compliance, preconstruction, and historic preservation. I am grateful to the colleagues, mentors, and teams who have contributed to my professional growth along the way.\nWhat drew me to Flock Safety is its mission of helping communities thrive through technology and public safety. I'm looking forward to applying my experience in construction and program management to support that mission while helping enable the company's continued growth across the country.\nThank you to everyone at Flock who made the interview and onboarding process such a positive experience, and to my colleagues at ICC COMMONWEALTH and DOMINION GLOBAL who have been an important part of my professional journey.\nI look forward to joining the team and beginning this next chapter.\n#FlockSafety #Operations #PublicSafety",
